<h1>About the Debian Installer</h1>

<p>
The Debian Installer is the replacement for boot-floppies, which will be
used to install future versions of Debian, beginning with sarge. It has
been designed to be more modular, easier to use, and more extensible
than the ageing boot-floppies.
</p>

